headline: J.B. Hunt Gears Up to Report Q3 Earnings: What's in the Cards?
summary: JBHT's third-quarter 2025 revenues are expected to decline year over year. Higher net interest expense might have hurt the bottom line.

headline: Unlocking Q3 Potential of JB Hunt (JBHT): Exploring Wall Street Estimates for Key Metrics
